prompts.frontCover:
A minimalist, humorous, and lighthearted birthday card front for Lao Lao. In the center, a flat 2D cartoon illustration features two people against a clean white background. On the left, a young East Asian woman (Lao Lao) with long, straight dark brown hair, round metal-framed glasses, and a warm, happy smile. She wears a light blue crewneck sweatshirt. Behind her, a young East Asian man (Jordan) with short, textured black hair embraces her, smiling broadly. He wears a tan hoodie. The illustration uses clean lines and simple shapes. Below the illustration, in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script, the text reads: "You're not old, you're just old enough to know better but still young enough to do it anyway. Happy Birthday, Lao Lao!"

- Reference photos provided for character creation
- Characters should only appear on the front cover
- Transform real people into artistic cartoon/illustrated versions matching the style
- Maintain recognizable features while adapting to the artistic style
